        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rIt is Friday the 13th, and Paris is hosting a spectacle of fashion and excess. Our client has identified five individuals whose continued existence they consider… unfortunate.\r\rThe terms are simple. All eliminations must be carried out while wearing the Vampire Magician outfit. Beyond that, the method is yours to choose.\r\rMaintaining subtlety may prove challenging, but it is not impossible.\r\rGood luck.",
